                </svg>
                Instagram
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <Section title="Frequently Asked Questions" backgroundColor="accent">
      <div class="space-y-lg">
        <div class="space-y-sm">
          <h3 class="text-h4 font-medium">How quickly do you respond to inquiries?</h3>
          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            I typically respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours during business days.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-sm">
          <h3 class="text-h4 font-medium">Do you offer virtual consultations?</h3>
          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            Yes! I'm happy to schedule virtual meetings via Zoom, Google Meet, or your preferred platform.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-sm">
          <h3 class="text-h4 font-medium">What areas do you serve for in-person lessons?</h3>
          <p class="text-body leading-relaxed">
            I currently offer in-person lessons in the greater Seattle area. For those outside this region, 
            virtual lessons are available.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </Section>
  </main>
</Layout> 